Metabrik::Repository
====================

   To know more: http://www.metabrik.org/blog/

INSTALLATION

   To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   This module requires these other programs and modules:

   A. For Debian-based systems:

   sudo
   mercurial
   apt-get
   cpanminus

   B. For FreeBSD systems

   pkg
   devel/mercurial
   devel/p5-App-cpanminus
   security/sudo

   C. For all systems

   Perl v5.6.1
   Metabrik
   File::Copy
   File::Path
   File::Spec
   POSIX

